Feature: User View Offer (Story 3)

	As a user
	So that I can redeem my offers
	I want to see my code, instructions and expiration date of my offers

Scenario: 

	Given that I am a user
	And I am on the offer page
	Then I should see the names of each vendor
	And I should see the codes of each vendor
	And I should see the instructions of each vendor
	And I should see the expiration date of each vendor